And that is the way
that modern physics

00:00:51.790 --> 00:00:55.420
conceives the nature of
matter and, in particular,

00:00:55.420 --> 00:00:58.540
the property of mass.

00:00:58.540 --> 00:01:00.910
So what I want to try
and do is to give you

00:01:00.910 --> 00:01:06.010
